  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Boil</strong> a kettle and preheat the oven to 230&deg;C/ 210&deg;C (fan)/ 450&deg;F/ Gas 8</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cut</strong> the potatoes into 2cm chunks, skin on, and peel and roughly chop the garlic&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> both to a pot, cover with boiled water by 5cm, bring to the boil on a high heat and cook for 10-15 min or until fork tender</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, bash the walnuts into small crumbs (either in their bag with a rolling pin or in a pestle and mortar)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Strip</strong> the thyme leaves from their stalks and chop finely&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tip: If the stalks are soft, then chop and use them too</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mix</strong> the walnuts, thyme and breadcrumbs on a plate and season generously with salt</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(4 tbsp)</span> plain flour to a shallow bowl and season with salt and pepper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Crack</strong> the egg into another shallow bowl and beat well</p>\r\n<p><strong>Slice</strong> the chicken breast<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> in half lengthways, laying your hand over the breasts and sawing through, forming 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">(4)</span> thin escalopes</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Check</strong> on your potatoes and drain once fork tender for step 7</p>\r\n<p><strong>Coat</strong> one escalope in the seasoned flour, tapping off any excess</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dip</strong> it in the egg and coat well, then roll it in the breadcrumbs and press it firmly down to coat evenly</p>\r\n<p><strong>Repeat</strong> with the remaining escalope<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(4 tbsp)</span> vegetable oil on a medium heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>When</strong> hot, add the crumbed chicken and cook on each side for 3 min</p>\r\n<p><strong>Transfer</strong> them to a baking tray and put them in the oven for a further 5 min or until cooked through</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Line the tray with foil to avoid mess</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/468.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
